day.%20The%20trailer%20promises%20high-octane%20action.%20Sunny%20Deol%20continues%20his%20busy%20schedule%20with%20upcoming%20projects%2C%20including%20Lahore%201947%20and%20Border%202.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Such%20incidents%20happen'%3A%20Minister's%20shocking%20remark%20after%20Bengaluru%20woman%20molested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744007996000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120055793%2Cimgsize-24156.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fsuch-incidents-happen-in-big-cities-karnataka-minister-g-parameshwaras-shocking-remark-over-bengaluru-womans-molestation%2Farticleshow%2F120055528.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20home%20minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20faced%20criticism%20for%20downplaying%20a%20molestation%20incident%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20calling%20such%20crimes%20common%20in%20big%20cities.%20The%20April%203rd%20incident%2C%20captured%20on%20CCTV%2C%20showed%20a%20man%20molesting%20a%20woman%20in%20Bharati%20Layout.%20Bengaluru%20police%20have%20filed%20a%20suo%20motu%20case%20and%20are%20working%20to%20locate%20the%20victim%20to%20formalize%20the%20complaint.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fsuch-incidents-happen-in-big-cities-karnataka-minister-g-parameshwaras-shocking-remark-over-bengaluru-womans-molestation%2Farticleshow%2F120055528.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Upstarts%20Or%20Startups%3F%20Why%20India%20Needs%20To%20Separate%20Men%20From%20Boys%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20a%20well-known%20yet%20an%20interesting%20fact%20that%20Vinod%20Khosla%2C%20often%20described%20as%20the%20hottest%20venture%20capitalist%20on%20the%20planet%20and%20a%20technology%20pioneer%20who%20was%20the%20founding%20CEO%20of%20Sun%20Microsystems%2C%20had%20relocated%20to%20Delhi%2C%20the%20city%20he%20grew%20up%20in%2C%20around%20the%20mid-1990s%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20his%20parents%2C%20not%20far%20from%20IIT%20Delhi%20where%20he%20studied.%20But%20the%20Internet%20opportunity%20that%20followed%20saw%20him%20move%20back%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20where%20he%20remains%20a%20cutting-edge%20figure%20in%20areas%20like%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20medical%20technology%20and%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20days%20tracking%20and%20meeting%20the%20man%20who%20now%20runs%20Khosla%20Ventures%20after%20leaving%20Kleiner%20Perkins%2C%20the%20VC%20firm%20that%20funded%20companies%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Google%2C%20came%20to%20mind%20last%20week%20as%20I%20heard%20the%20timely%20but%20controversial%20statement%20by%20India's%20commerce%20and%20industry%20minister%20at%20the%20'Startup%20Mahakumbh'%20jamboree.%20%26quot%3BAre%20we%20going%20to%20be%20happy%20being%20delivery%20boys%20and%20girls...%20Is%20that%20the%20destiny%20of%20India%3F%20This%20is%20not%20a%20startup%3B%20this%20is%20entrepreneurship...%20What%20the%20other%20side%20is%20doing%E2%80%94robotics%2C%20machine%20learning%2C%203D%20manufacturing%20and%20next%20generation%20factories%2C%26quot%3B%20Goyal%20said%2C%20showing%20a%20slide%20titled%20%E2%80%98India%20vs%20China.%20The%20Startup%20Reality%20Check'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20To%20Learn%20From%20Khosla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%E2%80%98startup'%20is%20often%20used%20loosely%2C%20but%20ideally%20should%20refer%20to%20technology-driven%20companies%20that%20can%20grow%20big%20through%20innovations.%20My%20view%20is%20that%20cutting-edge%20entrepreneurship%20is%20more%20about%20adventurous%20ambition%20than%20just%20growth.%20People%20like%20Khosla%20have%20a%20mental%20streak%20that%20shows%20passion%20for%20novelty%2C%20not%20mere%20get-rich-quick%20ideas.%20We%20need%20more%20like%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20wanting%20to%20be%20the%20entrepreneurial%20plumbers%20and%20builders%20of%20new%20technologies%20as%20such%2C%20but%20there%20is%20more%20to%20the%20future%20than%20that.%20When%20technology%20companies%20like%20Infosys%20were%20built%20in%20the%201980s%20and%201990s%2C%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98startup'%20was%20not%20even%20in%20vogue.%20But%20then%2C%20it%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20company%20to%20list%20on%20the%20tech-heavy%20Nasdaq%20exchange%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20subsequent%20rush%20of%20VCs%20in%20India%20became%20less%20about%20technology%20and%20more%20about%20demographics.%20India's%20surging%2C%20increasingly%20affluent%20population%20and%20an%20Internet%20boom%20made%20VCs%20fuel%20a%20greed%20to%20build%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98unicorn'%20startups%20that%20commanded%20a%20valuation%20of%20a%20billion%20dollars%20or%20more%20-%20usually%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20IPOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'This%20Of%20That'%20Culture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20had%20as%20a%20result%20was%20what%20tech%20investor%20Kashyap%20Deorah%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bthis%20of%20that%26quot%3B%20culture%3A%20Paytm%20became%20the%20PayPal%20of%20India%2C%20Flipkart%20was%20dubbed%20the%20Amazon%20of%20India%2C%20Swiggy%20and%20Zomato%20cloned%20Delivery%20Hero%20and%20Yelp%20with%20some%20tweaks.%20They%20mostly%20addressed%20a%20local%20market%20and%20built%20local%20brands%2C%20but%20not%20real%20intellectual%20property%20(IP)%20based%20on%20novelty%20on%20a%20global%20scale.%20That%20requires%20guts%20and%20an%20outlook%20of%20a%20different%20kind.%20Somewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20we%20started%20mistaking%20upstarts%20for%20startups.%20VCs%20and%20naive%20journalists%20fed%20into%20the%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20India%20has%20had%20real%20startups%20that%20are%20less%20celebrated.%20InMobi%2C%20a%20mobile%20ad%20platform%20that%20rivals%20Facebook-owner%20Meta%2C%20was%20hailed%20as%20India's%20first%20unicorn%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20an%20IPO%20this%20year%2C%20nearly%20two%20decades%20into%20its%20existence.%20InMobi%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20independent%20mobile%20ad%20network%2C%20engaging%20more%20than%20750%20million%20consumers%20across%20165%20countries.%20It%20is%20said%20to%20have%20turned%20down%20an%20acquisition%20offer%20from%20Google%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI-flex%20solutions%2C%20built%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20was%20acquired%20by%20Oracle%20for%20close%20to%20a%20billion%20dollars.%20It%20was%20a%20cutting-edge%20banking%20software%20company%20with%20a%20global%20footprint.%20Chennai-centred%20productivity%20software%20company%20Zoho%20competes%20with%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20are%20yet%20to%20produce%20a%20breathtaking%20product%20like%20Google.%20China%20is%20not%20quite%20there%20yet%2C%20either.%20But%20it%20is%20trying%20hard%20and%20big%2C%20as%20we%20have%20seen%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20DeepSeek%2C%20a%20disruptive%20AI%20model.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20has%20had%20a%20long%2C%20credible%20history%20of%20nurturing%20research%20through%20the%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20and%20other%20state-run%20bodies%20that%20set%20the%20base%20for%20cutting-edge%20innovation.%20Even%20ISRO%20and%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20have%20made%20quiet%20innovations.%20What%20we%20lack%20is%20new-age%20thinking%20by%20entrepreneurs%20that%20goes%20from%20ambition%20to%20adventure%20and%20closer%20innovation%20links%20with%20these%20establishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Steel%20Was%20Like%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20now%20raise%20a%20toast%20to%20the%20memory%20of%20Jamshedji%20Nusserwanji%20Tata%2C%20who%20dared%20to%20think%20of%20making%20steel%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20rural%20jungle%20in%20a%20colonially%20oppressed%20country%20in%201907.%20For%20the%20India%20of%20those%20times%2C%20steel%20was%20like%20AI.%20Verghese%20Kurien%20built%20Amul%20in%20rural%20Anand%20when%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98startup'%20did%20not%20exist%20in%20the%20Indian%20lexicon.%20The%20kind%20of%20adventurous%20streak%20shown%20in%20those%20ventures%20is%20something%20current%20entrepreneurs%20could%20learn%20from.%20Patience%2C%20patents%2C%20and%20perseverance%20separate%20the%20men%20from%20the%20boys%20and%20women%20from%20the%20girls%20in%20a%20true%20startup%20universe.%20Not%20scale%2C%20speed%20and%20salesmanship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20must%20be%20admitted%20that%20risk%20appetite%20requires%20context.%20You%20have%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20enough%20not%20to%20confuse%20a%20gamble%20with%20entrepreneurial%20chutzpah.%20We%20also%20need%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20a%20dubious%20culture%20of%20startup%20wannabes%20wanting%20corporate%20freebies%20from%20the%20government%20-%20from%20land%20to%20capital%20to%20subsidies.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20point%20to%20less-known%20Indian%20companies%20like%20Hyderabad-based%20MOSChip%20Technologies%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20field%20of%20semiconductors%20without%20being%20part%20of%20the%20VC-fuelled%20unicorn%20hype.%20Electric%20car%20maker%20Reva%2C%20founded%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20is%20now%20part%20of%20the%20Mahindra%20group%2C%20and%20deserves%20praise%20for%20its%20early%20start%20and%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20listed%20small-cap%20companies%20fall%20in%20that%20league.%20Intellect%20Design%20Arena%20and%20Nucleus%20Software%20have%20built%20products%20and%20intellectual%20property%2C%20but%20perhaps%20have%20not%20taken%20the%20big%20bets%20needed%20to%20capture%20glamorous%20headlines.%20They%20were%20never%20called%20startups%20but%20certainly%20were%20in%20the%20league%20when%20they%20started.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20Adventure%20Reign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20would%20like%20to%20see%20is%20some%20of%20India's%20200-plus%20US%20dollar%20billionaires%20throwing%20a%20hundred%20million%20dollars%20each%20at%20a%20patent-seeking%20team%20of%20cutting-edge%20innovators%20based%20on%20deep%20research.%20They%20all%20may%20not%20succeed%20or%20grow%20very%20big%2C%20but%20some%20will.%20Even%20more%20important%20in%20the%20current%20context%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20adventure%20that%20people%20like%20Vinod%20Khosla%2C%20rival%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20are%20famous%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20AI%20to%20quantum%20computing%20to%20genomics%2C%20opportunities%20for%20discovery%20and%20invention%20are%20separate%20from%20those%20based%20on%20scale%20and%20speed.%20New%20discoveries%20are%20ushering%20in%20new%20opportunities.%20The%20minister's%20timing%20is%20just%20right.%20China's%20DeepSeek%20is%20best%20seen%20not%20as%20an%20inspiration%20but%20as%20a%20wake-up%20call.%20As%20a%20nation%20in%20which%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20nurtured%20research%20and%20development%20in%20a%20colonially%20battered%2C%20impoverished%20country%2C%20we%20have%20no%20excuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Madhavan%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20senior%20editor%2C%20writer%20and%20columnist%20with%20more%20than%2030%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20having%20worked%20for%20Reuters%2C%20The%20Economic%20Times%2C%20Business%20Standard%2C%20and%20Hindustan%20Times%20after%20starting%20out%20in%20the%20Times%20of%20India%20Group.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744007640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fpinfla58_startup_625x300_07_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fupstarts-or-startups-why-india-needs-to-separate-men-from-boys-8105805%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cutting-edge%20entreprene