%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHBO%20selecting%20the%20local%20Four%20Seasons%20as%20its%20main%20set%20proved%20a%20boon%20to%20William%20%26quot%3BBill%26quot%3B%20Heinecke%2C%20the%20American-born%20Thai%20businessman%20who%20founded%20Minor%20International%20PCL%2C%20which%20owns%20the%20property.%20His%20personal%20fortune%20is%20estimated%20at%20%241.2%20billion%20according%20to%20the%20index%2C%20which%20is%20valuing%20his%20net%20worth%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20attention%20from%20the%20series%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20help%20the%20country%20reach%20a%20record%2040%20million%20visitors%20this%20year%2C%20up%20from%2035.5%20million%20in%202024%2C%20may%20be%20fleeting.%20The%20White%20Lotus%2C%20a%20show%20that%20dives%20into%20the%20dramas%20of%20the%20holidaying%20ultra-rich%20in%20luxury%20resorts%2C%20has%20moved%20onto%20a%20new%20location%20each%20season%20-%20previous%20series%20were%20shot%20in%20Sicily%20and%20Hawaii%20-%20underscoring%20the%20urgency%20to%20capitalise%20on%20what%20could%20be%20a%20short-lived%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20businessmen%20are%20happy%20to%20attach%20their%20companies'%20brands%20to%20the%20confronting%20plot%20that%20exposes%20the%20dark%20side%20of%20most%20characters%20-%20including%20a%20father%20who's%20traveling%20with%20his%20family%20and%20is%20constantly%20thinking%20of%20committing%20suicide%20and%20another%20guest%20who%20was%20planning%20the%20murder%20the%20resort%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20challenging%20plot%2C%20a%20deadly%20March%2028%20earthquake%20in%20neighboring%20Myanmar%20was%20expected%20to%20reduce%20international%20arrivals%20by%20as%20much%20as%2015%25%20over%20the%20following%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20plans%20and%20projections%20remain%20intact%2C%26quot%3B%20Heinecke%20said%20on%20April%201.%20His%20Bangkok-listed%20Minor%20International%20is%20set%20for%20a%20record%20net%20profit%20this%20year