ated%20for%20the%20measles%2C%20mumps%2C%20and%20rubella%20(MMR)%20vaccine%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funvaccinated-child-dies-texas-measles-cases-surge-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeasles%20outbreak%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20measles%20is%20the%20MMR%20vaccine%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20said%20in%20an%20X%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSecKennedy%2Fstatus%2F1908967854394982414%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%2C%20in%20which%20he%20said%20he%20visited%20the%20family%20of%20the%20second%20child%20in%20Texas%20who%20died%20after%20contracting%20the%20highly%20contagious%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20added%20in%20the%20post%20that%20he%20had%20deployed%20a%20team%20to%20supply%20pharmacies%20and%20clinics%20in%20Texas%20with%20MMR%20vaccines%20and%20other%20medicines%20in%20March%20to%20support%20the%20state%20during%20the%20outbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Texas%20Health%20Department%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dshs.texas.gov%2Fnews-alerts%2Ftexas-announces-second-death-measles-outbreak%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20child%20who%20died%20from%20measles%20was%20not%20vaccinated%20against%20the%20disease.%20The%20department%20added%20that%20481%20measles%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20children%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20Texas%20since%20late%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-confirmed-health-secretary-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20vocal%20critic%20of%20vaccines%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20he%20launched%20his%202024%20presidential%20bid%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-vaccines-cut-funding-fda-2024-democrats-doj-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evowed%20to%20cut%20funding%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20federal%20health%20agencies%20that%20regulate%20childhood%20vaccines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20during%20his%20January%20confirmation%20hearings%20to%20become%20health%20secretary%2C%20Kennedy%20was%20grilled%20on%20his%20views%20on%20vaccines%20by%20Sen.%20Bill%20Cassidy%2C%20the%20Louisiana%20Republican%20who%20heads%20the%20Senate%20health%20committee%20and%20has%20spent%20decades%20practicing%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECassidy%20finally%20voted%20in%20favor%20of%20Kennedy%20after%20receiving%20assurances%20from%20Kennedy%20and%20the%20Trump%20administration%20that%20they%20would%20work%20within%20existing%20vaccine%20systems%20and%20not%20remove%20vaccine%20guidance%20from%20government%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fopinion%2Frobert-f-kennedy-jr-measles-outbreak-call-action-all-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopinion%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Fox%20News%20in%20March%2C%20Kennedy%20said%20the%20MMR%20vaccine%20was%20%26quot%3Bcrucial%20to%20avoiding%20potentially%20deadly%20disease.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20stopped%20short%20of%20mandating%20the%20vaccine%2C%20writing%20in%20the%20op-ed%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20to%20vaccinate%20is%20a%20personal%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-recommends-vitamin-a-to-fight-measles-amid-outbreaks-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecommended%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-recommends-vitamin-a-to-fight-measles-amid-outbreaks-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Vitamin%20A%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20possible%20treatment%20for%20measles%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20balanced%20diet%20and%20good%20nutrition%20%26quot%3Bremains%20a%20best%20defense%20against%20most%20chronic%20and%20infectious%20illnesses.%26quot