0in%20aircraft.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20all%20of%20those.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20travel%20market%20offers%20huge%20untapped%20potential%20for%20local%20and%20foreign%20carriers%2C%20with%20a%20new%20middle%20class%20on%20the%20move%20and%20the%20government%20upgrading%20infrastructure%20including%20airports.%20Air%20India%20has%20sought%20to%20tap%20into%20that%20boom%2C%20placing%20a%20massive%20order%20two%20years%20ago%20for%20new%20aircraft%20with%20Airbus%20SE%20and%20Boeing%20to%20upgrade%20its%20fleet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20lounges%2C%20faster%20connection%20timings%20and%20more%20skilled%20ground%20employees%20are%20other%20elements%20that%20seek%20to%20improve%20both%20the%20profitability%20for%20the%20airline%20the%20passenger%20experience%20at%20its%20hubs%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Bengaluru%20and%20put%20the%20carrier%20back%20on%20the%20global%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20storied%20airline%20with%20close%20to%20a%20century%20of%20operation%20history%2C%20Air%20India%20has%20been%20brought%20under%20new%20ownership%20led%20by%20the%20Tata%20Group%2C%20which%20was%20among%20the%20aviation%20pioneers%20in%20the%20country.%20Upon%20taking%20over%2C%20the%20late%20Ratan%20Tata%20acknowledged%20in%20a%20statement%20in%20late%202021%20that%20%26quot%3Badmittedly%20it%20will%20take%20considerable%20effort%20to%20rebuild%20Air%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20there's%20an%20opportunity%20to%20%26quot%3Bregaining%20the%20image%20and%20reputation%20enjoyed%20in%20earlier%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20upgrades%20targeted%20by%20Wilson%20are%20better%20connection%20timings.%20For%20example%2C%20on%20a%20flight%20between%20Australia%20and%20Europe%2C%20a%20stopover%20in%20India%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20180%20minutes%2C%20compared%20with%20as%20long%20as%2010%20hours%20previously.%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20helped%20Air%20India%20lift%20the%20percentage%20of%20transit%20passengers%20to%20a%20high%20single%20digit%20from%20practically%20nothing%20previously%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilson%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20overall%20experience%20hasn't%20always%20met%20his%20requirements.%20Cabin%20interiors%20are%20often%20a%20mishmash%20of%20older%20and%20newer%20materials%2C%20and%20traveler%20accounts%20on%20social%20media%20are%20filled%20with%20unflattering%20reviews%20that%20include%20messy%20seats%20and%20unappetizing%20catering.%20A%20deep%20refresh%20would%20mean%20changing%20all%20of%20the%20lavatories%2C%20interior%20panels%2C%20carpets%2C%20curtains%20and%20improve%20the%20existing%20seats%20and%20in-flight%20entertainment%20systems%20wherever%20possible%2C%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20cases%20that%20we%20have%20not%20done%20as%20well%20as%20we%20could%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20Group%20now%20operates%20two%20airline%20brands%20-%20full%20service%20Air%20India%20and%20Air%20India%20Express.%20Wilson's%20ambition%20is%20to%20make%20the%20group%20a%20challenger%20to%20global%20heavyweights%20like%20Emirates%20in%20carrying%20India's%20international%20passenger%20traffic%20and%20make%20India's%20airports%20a%20choice%20of%20transit%20for%20passengers%20flying%20between%20both%20sides%20of%20India%20-%20now%20a%20business%20that%20heavily%20favors%20low-cost%20specialist%20IndiGo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20largest%20airline%2C%20IndiGo%20has%20aggressively%20pushed%20an%20expansion%20that%20now%20targets%20a%20global%20reach.%20The%20airline%20has%20placed%20orders%20for%20the%20Airbus%20A350s%20that%20will%20start%20to%20come%20by%202027%2C%20putting%20it%20in%20direct%20competition%20with%20Air%20India's%20own%20international%20routes.%20And%20the%20low-cost%20airline%20is%20set%20to%20induct%20Airbus%20321%20XLRs%20this%20year%2C%20giving%20it%20access%20to%20city%20pairs%20as%20far%20flung%20as%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilson%2C%20who%20