D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20embrace%20on%20a%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f35b25b8b41a9673fcc9e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERick%20and%20Chelsea%20reunite%20after%20Rick's%20trip%20to%20Bangkok.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20HBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c60069b3-0267-4d82-a04a-fe516ce5bc12%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20'The%20White%20Lotus'%20end%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20episode%2C%20Chelsea's%20words%20ring%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESritala%20and%20Jim%2C%20the%20resort's%20owners%2C%20return%20from%20Bangkok.%20Rick%20and%20Jim%20have%20a%20heated%20exchange%20over%20breakfast%2C%20in%20which%20Jim%20insults%20Rick's%20mother%20and%20Rick%20reverts%20back%20into%20revenge%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20in%20a%20fit%20of%20fury%20and%20despair%2C%20Rick%20shoots%20Jim%20in%20the%20chest.%20As%20Jim%20lies%20dying%20in%20Sritala's%20arms%2C%20she%20tells%20him%20Jim%20was%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20shootout%20between%20Rick%20and%20Sritala's%20two%20security%20guards%20ensues.%20Rick%20kills%20both%20guards%2C%20then%20turns%20around%20and%20sees%20Chelsea%20has%20been%20shot%20in%20the%20chest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20picks%20up%20her%20body%20and%20carries%20her%20across%20one%20of%20the%20property's%20ponds%2C%20Gaitok%20%E2%80%94%20the%20seemingly%20feckless%20security%20guard%20%E2%80%94%20shoots%20Rick%20in%20the%20back.%20Rick%20and%20Chelsea%20fall%20off%20the%20bridge%2C%20and%20their%20bodies%20slowly%20sink%20into%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmor%20fati%2C%20indeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245d6c3d3-16c7-4dff-a5ed-a8f8eece1636%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20season%20of%20simmering%20tensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dramatic%20culmination%20of%20season%20three%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20came%20after%20viewers%20had%20been%20set%20up%20with%20plenty%20of%20pairs%20and%20trios%20of%20people%20who%20would%20want%20to%20harm%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20there's%20Rick%2C%20who%20came%20to%20the%20hotel%20with%20his%20younger%20girlfriend%2C%20Chelsea%20%E2%80%94%20and%20with%20a%20vendetta%20to%20exact%20revenge%20on%20Jim%2C%20the%20man%20who%20he%20believes%20killed%20his%20father%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20there's%20Timothy%20Ratliff%2C%20the%20patriarch%20of%20a%20rich%20southern%20family%20whose%20big%20finance%20career%20is%20blowing%20up%20in%20front%20of%20his%20eyes.%20He%20repeatedly%20fantasizes%20about%20killing%20himself%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20his%20daughter%2C%20and%20his%20oldest%20son%20to%20spare%20them%20the%20shame%20of%20his%20professional%20sins.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20he%20even%20steals%20Gaitok's%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20actors%20Jason%20Isaacs%20and%20Parker%20Posey%20holding%20pina%20coladas%20on%20the%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f35c8663d72727e199561b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETimothy%20and%20Victoria%20Ratliff%20holding%20poisoned%20pina%20coladas%20in%20the%20season%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20HBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20of%20course%2C%20there's%20Gary.%20He's%20a%20threat%20to%20Belinda%2C%20a%20hotel%20staffer%20from%20season%20two%20who%20is%20now%20a%20hotel%20guest%20on%20a%20training%20rotation.%20Belinda%20discovers%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGary%20is%20wanted%20for%20questioning%20in%20relation%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehis%20wife%20Tanya's%20death%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(which%20was%20the%20dramatic%20end%20to%20season%20two%20of%20the%20show).%20Gary%20tries%20to%20buy%20Belinda%20off%20with%20a%20%24100%2C000%20payment%3B%20Belinda%20declines%20and%20says%20she%20needs%20time%20to%20consider%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20Gary's%20only%20vendetta.%20He's%20romantically%20involved%20with%20a%20woman%20named%20Chloe%20%E2%80%94%20who's%20beautiful%2C%20young%2C%20and%20capricious.%20After%20Chloe%20takes%20his%20yacht%20to%20entertain%20some%20friends%20for%20a%20full%20moon%20party%20that%20turns%20raunchy%20(and%20incestuous)%2C%20Gary%20believes%20Chloe%20slept%20with%20one%20of%20the%20two%20Ratliff%20sons%2C%20creating%20three%20potential%20targets%20for%20Gary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20actors%20Natasha%20Rothwell%20and%20Nicholas%20Duvernay%20sitting%20ona%20couch%20on%20the%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f35a5b63d72727e19955fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBelinda%20and%20Zion%20negotiate%20their%20terms%20with%20Gary.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20HBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227622f0f3-5ab2-4d3d-ab8d-53de78939840%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20world%20order%20%E2%80%94%20sort%20of%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20characters%2C%20the%20season%20ends%20with%20a%20new%20world%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20episode%2C%20both%20of%20Sritala's%20bodyguards%20are%20dead.%20Her%20newest%20appointment%3F%20Gaitok%20himself%2C%20now%20fitted%20out%20in%20a%20sleek%20black%20T-shirt%2C%20driving%20Sritala's%20shiny%20car%2C%20and%20getting%20a%20loving%20goodbye%20hug%20Mook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20has%20shown%20before%2C%20this%20is%20a%20show%20about%20how%20money%20lets%20rich%20people%20sail%20away%20from%20the%20world%20and%20from%20their%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20season%20is%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ratliff%20family%20departs%20from%20the%20resort%2C%20settling%20back%20into%20all%20the%20technology%20they%20had%20surrendered%20on%20vacation.%20Timothy%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20narrowly%20talked%20himself%20out%20of%20killing%20his%20family%20by%20way%20of%20poisoned%20pina%20coladas%20%E2%80%94%20vows%20they%20will%20get%20through%20anything%20that%20comes%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20Chloe%20flirting%20with%20a%20guy%20in%20a%20pool%20and%20gesturing%20back%20to%20Gary%2C%20who%20winks%20slyly%20%E2%80%94%20rich%20and%20untouched%20by%20his%20season%20two%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20most%20strikingly%2C%20we%20end%20the%20season%20with%20a%20view%20of%20the%20newest%20rich%20folks%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20orbit.%20Belinda%20didn't%20take%20Gary's%20%24100%2C000%20buyout%20%E2%80%94%20because%20she%20and%20her%20son%20Zion%20negotiated%20a%20%245%20million%20payday%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20season%20ends%20with%20Belinda%20and%20Zion%2C%20rich%20on%20blood%20money%2C%20literally%20sailing%20away%20into%20the%20sunset%20on%20a%20private%20speedboat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-lotus-season-3-ending-explained-who-dies-thailand-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744000428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f354d1b8b41a9673fcc997%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-lotus-season-3-ending-explained-who-dies-thailand-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20understand%20the%20events%20that%20unfold%20in%20the%20final%20episode%20of%20'The%20White%20Lotus%2C'%20look%20at%20the%20conversation%20Chelsea%20and%20Rick%20have%20over%20their%20last%20dinner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lina%20Batarags)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-lotus-season-3-ending-explained-who-dies-thaila