y%20shows.%20The%20studio%20in%20Khar%20subsequently%20shut%20down%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20exercises%20no%20control%20over%20the%20content%20of%20any%20show.%20Parts%20of%20the%20studio%20were%20demolished%20the%20next%20day%2C%20with%20civic%20authorities%20citing%20building%20law%20violations.%20But%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20action%20has%20sparked%20a%20buzz%20that%20the%20action%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20Kunal%20Kamra%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Kamra%20has%20stressed%20his%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYour%20inability%20to%20take%20a%20joke%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20a%20powerful%20public%20figure%20does%20not%20change%20the%20nature%20of%20my%20right.%20As%20far%20as%20I%20know%2C%20it%20is%20not%20against%20the%20law%20to%20poke%20fun%20at%20our%20leaders%20and%20the%20circus%20that%20is%20our%20political%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20said%20he%20was%20willing%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20police%20and%20courts%2C%20but%20has%20questioned%20if%20those%20involved%20in%20vandalising%20the%20studio%20will%20also%20face%20action.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20apologise.%20I%20don't%20fear%20this%20mob%20and%20I%20will%20not%20be%20hiding%20under%20my%20bed%2C%20waiting%20for%20this%20to%20die%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20has%20said%20he%20did%20not%20support%20the%20vandalism%2C%20but%20cited%20party%20workers'%20sentiments%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bevery%20action%20has%20a%20reaction%26quot%3B.%20He%20has%20also%20asked%20who%20gave%20Kunal%20Kamra%20%26quot%3Bsupari%26quot%3B%20to%20target%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743999420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F7203jt8o_no-notices-issued-to-the-audience-who-attended-kunal-kamras-show-mumbai-police_625x300_02_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomedian-kunal-kamra-approaches-bombay-high-court-over-fir-