011%20am%20to%204%20am%20the%20next%20morning.%20Seventeen%20hours%20on%20the%20trot.%20Surely%2C%20parliamentary%20democracy%20is%20all%20energised%20and%20in%20top%20form.%20Right%20%3F%20No.%20Completely%20wrong.%20Don't%20let%20the%20contrived%20all-night-long%20sessions%20deceive%20you.%20To%20borrow%20a%20sentence%20first%20used%20by%20columnist%20Vir%20Sanghvi%2C%20%E2%80%9CParliament%20is%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20deep%2C%20dark%20chamber%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Statutory%20Resolution%20to%20the%20Proclamation%20of%20President's%20Rule%20in%20Manipur%20was%20notified%20on%20February%2013%2C%202025.%20Parliament%20recommenced%20on%20March%2010.%20Why%20then%20was%20this%20discussion%20on%20Manipur%20held%20at%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20the%20session%3F%20%C2%A0Why%20was%20the%20Government%20avoiding%20the%20subject%20for%20almost%20three%20weeks%3F%20Worse%20still%2C%20why%20in%20the%20dead%20of%20night%3F%20Just%2044%20minutes%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20was%20even%20more%20jarring.%20Three%20hours%20had%20been%20allotted%20for%20the%20discussion.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20used%20just%20two%20minutes%20of%20the%2075%20minutes%20they%20were%20allotted.%20In%20fact%2C%20when%20the%20opening%20speaker%20from%20the%20BJP%20was%20just%20two%20minutes%20into%20his%20speech%2C%20floor%20leaders%20from%20his%20party%20shut%20him%20down.%20Indifference%20infinity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20more%20notes%20from%20the%20diary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Voting%20On%20The%20Waqf%20Bill%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20voting%20on%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Opposition%20ended%20up%20with%2095%20votes.%20If%20it%20wasn't%20for%20medical%20emergencies%2C%20a%20century%20might%20well%20have%20been%20scored.%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha's%20(JMM)%20Shibu%20Soren%20and%20Mahua%20Majhi%20were%20advised%20by%20doctors%20not%20to%20travel.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20from%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party(SP)%20and%20Subrata%20Bakshi%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(AITC)%20were%20also%20absent%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%20We%20wish%20them%20all%20a%20speedy%20and%20full%20recovery.%20Also%2C%20one%20vote%20from%20the%20Opposition%20was%20declared%20invalid%20due%20to%20a%20technicality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20No%20Deputy%20Speaker%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20session%20has%20ended%20and%20there%20is%20still%20no%20Deputy%20Speaker%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20It%20has%20now%20been%20almost%20300%20days%20since%20the%20current%20Lok%20Sabha%20commenced.%20Article%2093%20of%20the%20Constitution%20mandates%20the%20election%20of%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20may%20be%26quot%3B.%20Yet%2C%20a%20constitutional%20post%20continues%20to%20remain%20vacant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20No%20Notice%20From%20Opposition%20Accepted%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20a%20single%20notice%20raised%20by%20the%20Opposition%20was%20accepted%20for%20a%20discussion.%20The%20last%20time%20a%20notice%20from%20an%20Opposition%20MP%20was%20admitted%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20was%2016%20months%20ago%2C%20in%20December%202023%2C%20when%20this%20columnist%20raised%20the%20discussion%20on%20%E2%80%98The%20Economic%20Situation%20In%20The%20Country'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20parliamentary%20device%20used%20by%20MPs%20in%20the%20Opposition%20to%20hold%20the%20government%20accountable%20is%20a%20Calling%20Attention%20Motion%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Callows%20an%20MP%20to%20draw%20a%20Minister's%20attention%20to%20a%20matter%20of%20urgent%20public%20importance%E2%80%9D.%20The%20last%20Calling%20Attention%20was%20accepted%20in%20July%202024%2C%20on%20the%20floods%20in%20Kerala.%20Opposition%20parties%20pushed%20for%20discussion%20on%20issues%20like%20duplication%20of%20voter%20IDs%2C%20youth%20unemployment%2C%20amongst%20others.%20The%20government%20looked%20the%20other%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20The%20Opposition's%20New%20Tactic%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20being%20deprived%20of%20time%20to%20speak%20or%20when%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20raise%20issues%2C%20the%20Opposition%20resorted%20to%20a%20new%20tactic.%20Prolonged%20protests%20were%20replaced%20with%20short%20walkouts%20-%20these%20invariably%20lasted%20for%20about%2010%20to%2030%20minutes.%20The%20point%20was%20made%20and%20the%20MPs%20trooped%20back%20into%20the%20House%20to%20participate.%20Walk%20out%20and%20walk%20back.%20This%20columnist%20remembers%20this%20tactic%20from%20the%20late%20Sitaram%20Yechury's%20playbook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20The%20PM's%20Vote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20abroad%20when%20voting%20took%20place%20on%20the%20Waqf%20Bill.%20History%20will%20record%20that%20he%20did%20not%20support%20the%20Bill.%20Or%20oppose%20it.%20Or%20abstain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%C2%A0%20The%20LAMP%20Convocation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-eight%20MPs%2C%20across%2017%20parties%2C%20gathered%20at%20the%20India%20International%20Centre%2C%20Lodhi%20Road.%20The%20occasion%3A%20the%2015th%20annual%20convocation%20ceremony%20of%20young%20legislative%20assistants%20(interns)%20who%20had%20each%20spent%20one%20year%20with%20an%20MP%20they%20had%20been%20assigned%20to.%20Parliamentarians%20showered%20generous%20praise%20on%20the%20outgoing%20Legislative%20Assistants%20to%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20(LAMPs)%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20accompanied%20by%20their%20proud%20parents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Book%20Launches%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20there%20be%20a%20Parliament%20session%20without%20a%20book%20launch!%20Two%20DMK%20MPs%20launched%20their%20books.%20Tiruchi%20Siva%20published%20a%20collection%20of%20his%20WhatsApp%20good%20morning%20messages.%20His%20colleague%2C%20Dr%20T.%20Sumathy%2C%20launched%20her%20book%20%3Cem%3EBeatrice%20Webb%3A%20A%20Portrait%20of%20a%20Reformist%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Both%20books%20were%20launched%20at%20different%20locations%20on%20the%20same%20day%20at%20the%20same%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Who%20Captained%20The%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20was%20the%20Government's%20headliner%20this%20session.%20He%20piloted%20three%20bills%20from%20his%20Ministry%20and%20also%20spoke%20for%2045%20minutes%20on%20Waqf%2C%20which%20he%20did%20not%20pilot.%20Amit%20Shah%20was%20BJP's%20batsman%2C%20bowler%20and%20fielder.%20For%20a%20change%2C%20he%20%C2%A0was%20also%20seen%20more%20than%20once%20in%20the%20cafeteria%2C%20interacting%20with%20MPs%20across%20parties.%20Interesting%20times.%20As%20a%20colleague%20observed%2C%20is%20it%20the%20240%20effect%3F%20Or%20could%20it%20be%20a%2052%20year-old%20bachelor%20captaining%20a%20very%20large%20state.%20Keen%20contest.%20Watch%20this%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743996180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fubn369d_rajya-sabha-waqf_625x300_03_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fparliament-session-dont-let-the-all-nighters-deceive-you-8104913%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20borrow%20a%20sentence%20first%20used%20by%20columnist%20Vir%20Sanghvi%2C%20%26quot%3BParliament%20is%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20deep%2C%20dark%20chamber%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Don't%20like%20them%20bombing%20on%20and%20on'%3A%20Trump%20on%20Russia-Ukraine%20peace%20talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743995901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120051396%2Cimgsize-730807.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdont-like-them-bombing-on-and-on-trump-responds-to-question-on-russia-ukraine-peace-talks%2Farticleshow%2F120051320.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20calls%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20urging%20Vladimir%20Putin%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20Amid%20increased%20Russian%20attacks%20and%20a%20plea%20from%20Ukrainian%20President%20Zelenskyy%2C%20French%20President%20Macron%20emphasizes%20the%20need%20for%20strong%20actions%20if%20Russia%20continues%20aggression%2C%20highlighting%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20and%20civilian%20casualties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdont-like-them-bombing-on-and-on-trump-responds-to-question-on-russia-ukraine-peace-talks%2Farticleshow%2F120051320.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhoni%20Sent%20Brutal%20Message%20Amid%20IPL%20Struggle%3A%20'Should've%20Left%20Long%20Back...'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnce%20labelled%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98finisher'%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20MS%20Dhoni%20is%20under%20serious%20pressure%20after%20failing%20to%20contribute%20to%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings'%20run%20chase%20for%20a%20third%20straight%20game%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20season.%20The%20five-time%20champions%20started%20the%20season%20with%20a%20four-wicket%20win%20over%20Mumbai%20Indians%20but%20have%20since%20lost%20in%20three%20straight%20games%2C%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20and%20Delhi%20Capitals%20respectively%20while%20chasing%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20them%20fall%20down%20to%20the%20ninth%20spot%20in%20the%20league%20table.%20The%20former%20India%20captain%20still%20looks%20as%20quick%20as%20ever%20behind%20the%20stumps%20but%20has%20batted%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20138.18%2C%20down%20from%20220.55%20in%20the%20previous%20edition%2C%20while%20struggling%20to%20find%20the%20boundaries%20and%20score%20at%20a%20quick%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20conversation%20with%20IANS%2C%20former%20Pakistan%20captain%20Rashid%20Latif%20stated%20that%20Dhoni%20should%20have%20left%20the%20game%20a%20while%20back%20and%20being%20a%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20himself%2C%20he%20believes%20the%20role%20should%20now%20be%20passed%20on%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20should%20have%20left%20a%20long%20while%20back%2C%20a%20wicket-keeper's%20age%20is%20usually%2035%2C%20I%20am%20an%20example%20of%20this.%20If%20I%20was%20on%20TV%20then%20I%20am%20a%20performer%20and%20when%20I%20don't%20do%20it%20at%20a%20high%20level%20then%20my%20reputation%20will%20come%20down.%20Even%20if%20you%20have%20done%20it%20for%2015%20years%2C%20the%20younger%20generations%20will%20not%20be%20impressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Latif%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatif%20further%20added%20by%20saying%20Chennai%20choosing%20Dhoni%20over%20the%20team%20%E2%80%98is%20unfair%20to%20the%20game%20of%20cricket'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20playing%20did%20not%20benefit%20his%20team%20in%202019%20(ODI%20World%20Cup)%20as%20well%2C%20they%20should%20have%20understood%20then.%20If%20you%20are%20choosing%20the%20team%20over%20one%20player%20then%20it%20is%20unfair%20to%20the%20game%20which%20is%20why%20they%20are%20getting%20trolled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%202-3%20games%20and%20the%20crowd%20gets%20very%20loud%20but%20CSK%20need%20points%20right%20now%2C%20they%20are%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20table%20and%20if%20the%20reason%20is%20only%20one%20or%20two%20players%20then%20you%20should%20realise%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20Dhoni's%20possible%20retirement%2C%20after%20the%20loss%20against%20Delhi%2C%20Chennai%20head%20coach%20Stephen%20Fleming%20refused%20to%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20stated%20he%20has%20%E2%80%98no%20idea'%20when%20the%20legendary%20player%20will%20consider%20hanging%20up%20his%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20that's%20not%20my%20role%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it.%20I%20have%20no%20idea.%20I'm%20just%20enjoying%20working%20with%20him%20still.%20He's%20still%20going%20strong.%20I%20don't%20even%20ask%20these%20days.%20You%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20ask%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Fleming%20in%20the%20post-game%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743995280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fa1lfmsb_ms-dhoni-bcci_625x300_06_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fms-dhoni-sent-brutal-message-by-pakistan-great-amid-ipl-2025-struggle-shouldve-left-long-back-8101500%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20labelled%20as%20the%20finisher'%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20MS%20Dhoni%20is%20under%20serious%20pressure%20after%20failing%20to%20contribute%20to%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings'%20run%20chase%20for%20a%20third%20straight%20game%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fms-dhoni-sent-brutal-message-by-pakistan-great-amid-ipl-2025-struggle-shouldve-left-long-back-8101500%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saudi%20Arabia%20bans%20visas%20for%2014%20countries%20ahead%20of%20Hajj%3A%20Why%20is%20India%20on%20the%20list%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743995233000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120051156%2Cimgsize-126520.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Ftravel%2Fnews%2Fsaudi