%20you%20are%20consistently%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20a%20doubt%20grows%20in%20your%20mind%20(on%20him%20being%20dropped)%20but%20I%20cheered%20myself%20up%20and%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20execute%20what%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20deliver%2C%20you%20stay%20at%20the%20top.%20When%20you%20move%20the%20ball%20both%20in%20and%20out%20and%20it%20works%20instinctively%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20a%20different%20feeling.%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20was%20delighted%20that%20he%20could%20perform%20so%20well%20with%20his%20parents%20watching%20him%20from%20the%20stands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20come%20to%20your%20home%20ground%2C%20it's%20a%20special%20feeling.%20My%20family%20was%20there%20in%20the%20crowd%20and%20that%20lifted%20me%20up.%20I%20have%20played%20seven%20years%20for%20RCB.%20I%20have%20worked%20hard%20on%20my%20bowling%20and%20also%20on%20my%20mindset%2C%20it's%20working%20really%20well%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBowling%20first%2C%20GT%20restricted%20SRH%20to%20152%20for%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGill%20praises%20bowlers%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Titans%20skipper%20Shubman%20Gill%20lavished%20praise%20on%20his%20bowlers%20after%20their%20comfortable%20victory%20over%20hosts%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%2C%20terming%20them%20%26quot%3Bgame-changers%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20shortest%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBowlers%20are%20game-changers%2C%20especially%20in%20this%20format.%20Lot%20of%20people%20talk%20about%20T20s%2C%20batting%20and%20hitting%2C%20but%20we%20think%20matches%20are%20won%20by%20bowlers%20and%20that%20is%20why%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20emphasis%20on%20bowlers%20(in%20this%20franchise).%26quot%3B%20Gill%20led%20from%20the%20front%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20remaining%20not%20out%20on%2061%20off%2043%20balls.%20The%20skipper%20was%20also%20pleased%20to%20see%20the%20talented%20Washington%20Sundar%20excelling%20on%20GT%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Washington)%20was%20very%20close%20(to%20playing)%20in%20the%20game%20against%20Mumbai.%20He%20was%20padded%20the%20whole%20game%2C%20but%20with%20the%20impact%20player%20rule%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20an%20opportunity%20to%20play%20someone%20else%20(if%20you%20need%20an%20extra%20bowler)%2C%26quot%3B%20Gill%20said%20of%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20all%20about%20having%20a%20good%20partnership%2C%20and%20we%20said%20once%20we%20are%20set%2C%20we%20will%20take%20it%20from%20there.%26quot%3B%20About%20Siraj%2C%20Gill%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20energy%20he%20brings%20is%20tremendous.%20When%20playing%20against%20him%2C%20you%20want%20him%20in%20your%20team.%20His%20energy%20is%20infectious.%26quot%3B%20On%20his%20part%2C%20Washington%20said%20the%20advice%20from%20his%20captain%20was%20to%20take%20the%20game%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSkipper%20kept%20telling%20me%20to%20play%20as%20deep%20as%20possible.%20Got%20off%20to%20a%20good%20start%20and%20wanted%20to%20bat%20as%20deep%20as%20possible%20and%20finish%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20the%20trend%20in%20Hyderabad%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20In%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20the%20wicket%20gets%20better%20and%20easier%20to%20chase%20160-170%20on%20the%20board.%20I%20was%20well%20aware%20of%20it%20and%20it%20helped%20me.%26quot%3B%20SRH%20skipper%20Pat%20Cummins%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20a%20traditional%20Hyderabad%20wicket%2C%20tough%20to%20get%20fluency%20in%20your%20innings.%20At%20the%20end%20there%2C%20it%20did%20not%20spin%20as%20much%20as%20we%20thought.%20A%20few%20(runs)%20short%20and%20they%20batted%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A174399180