rsonal%20mirroring%20going%20on%20%5Bwith%20Walton%5D.%20We've%20not%20had%20the%20same%20lives%20as%20them%2C%20but%20everyone's%20essence%20is%20pretty%20similar%20to%20their%20character%20%E2%80%94%20apart%20from%20Patrick%20%5BSchwarzenegger%5D.%20He's%20nothing%20like%20Saxon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Wood%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Isaacs%2C%20who%20plays%20Timothy%20Ratliff%2C%20told%20Vulture%20there%20was%20some%20%26quot%3Bdrama%26quot%3B%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20a%20cross%20between%20summer%20camp%20and%20%3Cem%3ELord%20of%20the%20Flies%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20in%20a%20gilded%20cage.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20holiday%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20March.%20%26quot%3B%20Some%20people%20got%20very%20close%2C%20there%20were%20friendships%20that%20were%20made%20and%20friendships%20that%20were%20lost.%20All%20the%20things%20you%20would%20imagine%20with%20a%20group%20of%20people%20unanchored%20from%20their%20home%20lives%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20world%2C%20in%20the%20intense%20pressure%20cooker%20of%20the%20working%20environment%20with%20eye-melting%20heat%20and%20insects%20and%20late%20nights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20in%20Thailand%20stays%20in%20Thailand%2C%20but%20there's%20an%20off-screen%20White%20Lotus%20as%20well%2C%20with%20fewer%20deaths%20but%20just%20as%20much%20drama%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaacs%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-white-lotus-aimee-lou-wood-interview-cast-method-acting-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743971839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f2d71463d72727e1995347%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-white-lotus-aimee-lou-wood-interview