inability%20of%20menstrual%20management%2C%20applying%20what%20she%20calls%20the%20PASS%20model%20%E2%80%94%20Paryavaran%20(Environment)%2C%20Arthik%20(Economics)%2C%20Swasthya%20(Health)%2C%20and%20Samaj%20(Society)%20%E2%80%94%20to%20assess%20menstrual%20products%20holistically.%20%E2%80%9CA%20menstrual%20product%20has%20to%20be%20sustainable%20and%20viable%20from%20these%20four%20angles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20gone%20global.%20Her%20NGO%2C%20Jatan%20Sansthan%2C%20and%20her%20studio%2C%20Vikalpdesign%2C%20have%20welcomed%20design%20students%20from%20across%20the%20country%20for%20rural%20immersion%20programmes.%20These%20students%20go%20to%20the%20fields%2C%20sketch%2C%20analyse%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20seen%2C%20and%20compare%20it%20with%20their%20own%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Vikalpdesign%2C%20Lakshmi%20mentors%20students%20to%20co-create%20health%20visuals%20by%20immersing%20in%20rural%20realities%20and%20community%20dialogue.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22