Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Setting%20up%20the%20culture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Choose%20shallow%2C%20stagnant%20water%20bodies%20such%20as%20ponds%2C%20tanks%2C%20or%20ditches.%20You%20can%20also%20grow%20it%20in%20containers%20if%20space%20is%20limited.%20The%20depth%20should%20not%20exceed%2030-40%20cm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Temperature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Azolla%20grows%20best%20in%20warm%20conditions%2C%20with%20an%20ideal%20temperature%20range%20of%2025-30%C2%B0C.%20Avoid%20growing%20it%20in%20water%20temperatures%20below%2020%C2%B0C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-01T171907.733_11zon-1743508202.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-01T171907.733_11zon-1743508202.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-01T171907.733_11zon-1743508202-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-01T171907.733_11zon-1743508202-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-01T171907.733_11zon-1743508202-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-01T171907.733_11zon-1743508202-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417279%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGrowing%20azolla%20requires%20minimal%20investment%20and%20multiples%20quickly.%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2